Sentencas: A novel in situ co-assembled nanocomposite LSM-Bi1.6Er0.4O3 (ESB) (icn-LSMESB) was obtained by conjugated wet-chemical synthesis.
Titulo: Rational Design of Lower-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes via Nanotailoring of Co-Assembled Composite Structures

Titulo: Rational Design of Lower-Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cell Cathodes via Nanotailoring of Co-Assembled Composite Structures
